the sinking of the warship Cheonan that killed 46 South Korean sailors and an artillery strike on a South Korean island that killed four people.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.99767541173983, \"rank\": 0.0023299986882254803, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheonan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.934826758264397e-20, \"text\": \"Cheonan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheonan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheonan\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9878619711353515, \"rank\": 0.012286107253847768, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9878619711353515, \"rank\": 0.012286107253847768, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Details of the delegation's itinerary were not immediately available.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also not clear where the delegation would sit during the ceremony - a significant issue given the events of two weeks ago at the opening.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There, Kim Yo Jong sat in the same VIP box with Moon and U.S. Vice President Mike Pence, creating some awkward moments.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1917, \"enti